\cf0\b0 - Ph\u7847?n M\'f4 t\u7843? vi ph\u7841?m chi ti\u7871?t: th\u7921?c ra chi ti\u7871?t \f1\'f0\u432?\u7907?c th\u7875? hi\u7879?n \u7903? c\'e1c \'f4 b\f0\'ean d\lang1066\f2\'fd\u7899?i: lo\'e0i vi ph\u7841?m, h\lang1033\f0\'ecnh th\u7913?c vi ph\u7841?m, s\u7889? l\lang1066\f2\'fd\u7907?ng...V\u7853?y m\u7909?c n\'e0y n\'ean b\u7887?, ho\u7863?c \'f0\u7875? l\'e0 c\'e1c Th\'f4ng tin kh\'e1c v\'e0 \'f0\u7875? b\'ean d\'fd\u7899?i\lang1033\f0  \cf1\b --> Chuy\u7875?n m\'f4 t\u7843? vi ph\u7841?m th\'e0nh th\'f4ng tin kh\'e1c\lang1066\f2\par
\cf0\b0 - Tuy\u7871?n \'f0\'fd\u7901?ng: N\'ean \'f0\u7875?: T\u7915?....\'f0\u7871?n..., c\'f3 th\u7875? s\u7869? t\u7889?t h\'f5n cho vi\u7879?c th\u7889?ng k\'ea tuy\u7871?n v\u7853?n chuy\u7875?n h\'f5n ko? V\lang1033\f0\'ec ph\u7847?n n\'e0y \f1\'f0\u7875? ph\u7909?c v\u7909? vi\u7879?c sau n\f0\'e0y tra c\u7913?u theo tuy\u7871?n v\u7853?n chuy\u7875?n (anh li\'ean h\u7879? th\'eam anh Ninh b\'ean C\u7843?nh s\'e1t M\'f4i tr\lang1066\f2\'fd\u7901?ng h\'f4m tr\'fd\u7899?c tham d\u7921? h\u7885?p \'f0\u7875? h\u7887?i th\'eam)\lang1033\f0  -->\b  \cf1 S\u7869? chuy\u7875?n th\'e0nh t\u7915? v\'e0 \u273?\u7871?n \u273?\u7875? d\u7877? th\u7889?ng k\'ea\lang1066\f2\par
