3, K\u7871?t qu\u7843? x\u7917? l\'fd\par
- Th\u7901?i gian x\u7917? l\'fd: \'f0\u7875? kh\'f4ng ph\f0\'f9 h\u7907?p, v\'ec ko hi\u7875?u \f1\'f0i\u7873?n th\u7901?i gian di\u7877?n ra phi\f0\'ean t\'f2a, hay k\'ea phi\u7871?u ph\u7841?t. C\'f3 l\u7869? ch\u7881? \f1\'f0\u7875? muc th\u7901?i gian: t\u7893?ng th\u7901?i gian x\u7917? l\'fd xong v\u7909? vi\u7879?c \u7903? ph\u7847?n cu\u7889?i (Ph\u7847?n n\f0\'e0y anh li\'ean h\u7879? h\u7887?i th\'eam ch\u7883? H\u7857?ng b\'ean Vi\u7879?n Ki\u7875?m s\'e1t) --> \cf1\b Th\u7901?i gian x\u7917? l\'fd l\'e0 th\u7901?i gian t\'f9y \u273?\u417?n v\u7883? x\u7917? l\'fd m\'e0 c\'f3: v\'ed d\u7909? v\u7899?i c\u417? quan c\'f4ng an th\'ec l\'e0 th\u7901?i gian chuy\u7875?n h\u7891? s\u417? cho vi\u7879?n ki\u7875?m s\'e1t, v\u7899?i c\u417? quan vi\u7879?n ki\u7875?m s\'e1t th\'ec l\'e0 th\u7901?i gian chuy\u7875?n h\u7891? s\u417? cho t\'f2a \'e1n \u273?\u7875? k\u7871?t \'e1n, v\u7899?i c\u417? quan l\'e0 t\'f2a \'e1n th\'ec th\u7901?i gian l\'e0 th\u7901?i gian di\u7877?n ra phi\'ean t\'f2a. N\'ean ghi th\u7901?i gian x\u7917? l\'fd l\'e0 ghi chung.\par
